quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  4,172,Messiah nunquam disdain ex est servus DEUS nor would closest angels. Those qui disdain ex worshipping Eum est too arrogant submit He summon them totus ante Eum
  4,173,Prout pro those believe lead righteous vita He fully recompense them shower them His gratia! Prout pro those disdain turn arrogant He commit them painful retribution! They non invenit dominus DEUS nor savior
  4,174,O people proof advenit vos tuus Dominus; nos sent vos profound beacon
  4,175,Those believe in DEUS habuit fast Eum He admit them mercy Eum gratia guide them Eum in straight path
  4,176,They consult vos; dictus DEUS advises vos single person. Unus abiit non sinister infans he habet soror she gets semi inheritance! she abiit primas he inherits eam she non sinister infans. ibi est 2 soror they get two-thirds inheritance. siblings est vir femina vir gets twice share femina. DEUS sic clarifies vos lest vos iit astray! DEUS est fully aware de TOTUS things